    <sec id="sec22">
      <title>The detection of accelerated evolution</title>
      <p>The CGB provides a module to detect branch-specific accelerated evolution of SARS-CoV-2. We found that within 186,746 internal branches with <inline-formula><tex-math notation="LaTeX" id="ineq14">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
